{"word":"H8319 - שָׁרַק - shâraq - shaw-rak' - Hiss","slug":"H8319","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׁרַק</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>shâraq"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>shaw-rak'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Hiss"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05E8;&#x05E7; - sha&#x0302;raq</b> - <i>shaw-rak'</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to <i>be shrill</i>, that is, to whistle or <i>hiss</i> (as a call or in scorn): - hiss."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H8292\">H8292</a>, <a href=\"#/H8322\">H8322</a>"}]}